    {
      "text": "1. **Enhanced Metadata Loading**: Similar to plan commands, load request and plan metadata from database\n2. **Flow Step Tracking**: Add flow_step field to changeset schema and registration\n3. **Portal Detection**: Extract portal information from branch/repo context\n4. **Status Display**: Show approval/rejection status prominently\n5. **Link Formatting**: Use markdown-style links for request/plan references\n\n## Database Schema Changes\n\nAdd to `changesets` table:\n\n- `request_title` TEXT (derived from request metadata)\n- `plan_id` TEXT (link to plan)\n- `flow_id` TEXT (if created by flow)\n- `flow_step` TEXT (step description)\n- `portal_name` TEXT (explicit portal tracking)\n\n## Files to Modify",
